19
00:02:08,761 --> 00:02:11,261
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu, ampuni aku./
Cepat.</font>

20
00:02:11,631 --> 00:02:13,561
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau melakukannya atau tidak?
Kau melakukannya?</font>

21
00:02:13,561 --> 00:02:16,161
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takkan mengulanginya lagi./
Kemari kau.</font>

22
00:02:16,361 --> 00:02:17,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat.</font>

23
00:02:18,261 --> 00:02:19,591
<font color=#FFFF00>Ampuni aku.</font>

24
00:02:19,591 --> 00:02:22,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak mau menuruti
Ibu? Kenapa?</font>

25
00:02:23,661 --> 00:02:26,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita tak punya banyak waktu. Bicara padaku.</font>

26
00:02:26,361 --> 00:02:28,061
<font color=#FFFF00>Katamu kau dengar suara xylophone.</font>

27
00:02:28,061 --> 00:02:29,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mendengarnya...,</font>

28
00:02:29,661 --> 00:02:31,131
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku tidak tahu
suara apa itu sebenarnya.</font>

29
00:02:31,131 --> 00:02:33,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Katamu kau bisa tahu segalanya
dari mendengar suara.</font>

30
00:02:34,361 --> 00:02:36,261
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengar baik-baik.</font>

31
00:02:36,531 --> 00:02:37,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau menemukan lokasi dia...,</font>

32
00:02:37,961 --> 00:02:39,801
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan kupastikan
aku menyelamatkannya.</font>

33
00:02:40,261 --> 00:02:41,591
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, berkonsentrasilah.</font>

34
00:02:43,231 --> 00:02:45,931
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak tahu, aku belum pernah
dengar suara itu sebelumnya.</font>

35
00:02:45,931 --> 00:02:48,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu, ampuni aku./
Berhenti menangis.</font>

36
00:02:48,291 --> 00:02:50,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti menangis. Berhenti.</font>

37
00:02:51,161 --> 00:02:53,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Diam kau./
Ampuni aku, Ibu.</font>

38
00:02:54,091 --> 00:02:56,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Bicaralah pada wanita itu...</font>

39
00:02:56,261 --> 00:02:58,631
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan ulur waktu sebanyak mungkin. Paham?</font>

40
00:03:04,631 --> 00:03:06,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku./
Diamlah.</font>

41
00:03:11,961 --> 00:03:13,331
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah terlambat buat minta maaf.</font>

42
00:03:14,391 --> 00:03:15,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, ini belum terlambat.</font>

43
00:03:24,261 --> 00:03:25,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?</font>

44
00:03:28,091 --> 00:03:29,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa kau?</font>

45
00:03:30,661 --> 00:03:32,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini Kang Kwon Joo dari
112 Emergency Call Center.</font>

46
00:03:32,831 --> 00:03:34,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Polisi sedang menuju kesana.</font>

47
00:03:34,761 --> 00:03:35,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

48
00:03:42,391 --> 00:03:44,061
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak tahu aku
ada dimana.</font>

49
00:03:44,391 --> 00:03:46,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bercanda!/
Kami telah melacak ponsel Anda.</font>

50
00:03:46,791 --> 00:03:48,161
<font color=#FFFF00>Belum terlambat sekarang.</font>

51
00:03:48,161 --> 00:03:49,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Anda menyerahkan diri ke polisi,
hukuman Anda bisa diringankan.</font>

52
00:03:49,761 --> 00:03:50,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong...</font>

53
00:03:51,061 --> 00:03:52,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Demi Ah Ram...,</font>

54
00:03:53,591 --> 00:03:54,891
<font color=#FFFF00>...bersikap bijaksanalah.</font>

55
00:03:58,631 --> 00:04:01,061
<font color=#FFFF00>Suaranya seperti suara xylophone.
Cari suara itu.</font>

56
00:04:01,791 --> 00:04:03,561
<font color=#FFFF00>Mainan bayi? Alat tiup?</font>

57
00:04:03,561 --> 00:04:06,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukannya ada juga
mainan yang suaranya mirip xylophone?</font>

58
00:04:06,661 --> 00:04:08,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih spesifik lagilah.</font>

59
00:04:08,491 --> 00:04:10,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahulah, mainan anak-anak.</font>

60
00:04:11,131 --> 00:04:13,861
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harusnya tahu banyak, kau itu
seorang Ayah. Mana aku tahu suara apa itu?</font>

61
00:04:13,861 --> 00:04:15,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau itu harus bertindak
sebagai polisi.</font>

62
00:04:20,561 --> 00:04:24,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Dae Shik, apa kau ingat saat kita
dalam penyamaran...</font>

63
00:04:24,861 --> 00:04:26,191
<font color=#FFFF00>...di Myeonghwa-dong?</font>

64
00:04:27,131 --> 00:04:29,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku salah dengar bunyi gemerincing lonceng
rumah sebagai suara xylophone?</font>

65
00:04:29,231 --> 00:04:30,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku ingat.</font>

66
00:04:30,661 --> 00:04:33,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau marah karena suaranya terlalu keras.</font>

67
00:04:39,231 --> 00:04:41,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, tidak mungkin itu, Hyung.</font>

68
00:04:42,491 --> 00:04:43,561
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikut aku.</font>

69
00:04:47,331 --> 00:04:48,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Ahjussi.</font>

70
00:04:50,331 --> 00:04:51,831
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Boleh aku bertanya?</i></font>

71
00:04:52,331 --> 00:04:55,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada anak 7 tahun tinggal
di unit 406, Building 3?</font>

72
00:04:56,361 --> 00:04:57,861
<font color=#FFFF00>Unit 406, Building 3.</font>

73
00:04:59,131 --> 00:05:01,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tempat tinggalnya Ibu Jae Eun.</font>

74
00:05:01,931 --> 00:05:03,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi mereka cuma
punya satu anak perempuan.</font>

75
00:05:04,191 --> 00:05:07,991
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak itu dirawat di RS karena meningitis.</font>

76
00:05:08,231 --> 00:05:10,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Cuma punya anak perempuan?/
Ya.</font>

77
00:05:11,061 --> 00:05:12,931
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih atas kerjasamanya.</font>

78
00:05:14,231 --> 00:05:18,101
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jin Gu Hyung memberitahuku...</i></font>

79
00:05:18,291 --> 00:05:20,631
<font color=#FFFF00>...kalau ada anak perempuan
yang ada disini sebelum aku.</font>

80
00:05:20,691 --> 00:05:22,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi dia juga sangat sakit...,</font>

81
00:05:23,461 --> 00:05:24,991
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...jadi dia ada di rumah sakit.</i></font>

82
00:05:26,831 --> 00:05:28,391
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami menemukan pemilik ponsel tersebut.</font>

83
00:05:31,191 --> 00:05:32,991
<font color=#FFFF00>Choi Byung Wook./
<i>Pria, usia 30 tahun.</i></font>

84
00:05:32,991 --> 00:05:36,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Lima tahun lalu, usaha restorannya
di Burim-dong bangkrut.</font>

85
00:05:36,131 --> 00:05:39,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya dia kini
menjadi Chef di sebuah restoran.</font>

86
00:05:39,361 --> 00:05:41,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia mengadopsi 3 anak
hingga sekarang ini.</font>

87
00:05:41,131 --> 00:05:43,231
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak pertama meninggal dan anak kedua
dirawat di RS.</font>

88
00:05:43,231 --> 00:05:45,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya dia sekarang hanya tinggal bersama
anak lelaki yang diadopsinya tahun lalu.</font>

89
00:05:45,791 --> 00:05:47,331
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa alamatnya?</font>

90
00:05:47,331 --> 00:05:49,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Unit 406, Builiding 3, Dabok Villa.</font>

91
00:05:49,531 --> 00:05:51,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Nama istrinya Oh Soo Jin.</font>

92
00:05:52,331 --> 00:05:53,691
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala Center Kang.</font>

93
00:05:57,591 --> 00:05:58,931
<font color=#FFFF00>Kirimkan itu ke tim lapangan.</font>

94
00:05:58,931 --> 00:05:59,991
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

95
00:06:08,761 --> 00:06:09,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo.</font>

96
00:06:10,031 --> 00:06:11,931
<font color=#FFFF00>Disini!</font>

97
00:06:12,861 --> 00:06:14,991
<font color=#FFFF00>Di Building 3! Cepat!</font>

98
00:06:15,091 --> 00:06:18,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami sedang menuju Building 3.
Ulur waktu sebanyak mungkin.</font>

99
00:06:18,891 --> 00:06:19,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Disini!</font>

100
00:06:20,761 --> 00:06:22,091
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Soo Jin-ssi.</font>

101
00:06:22,461 --> 00:06:24,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Tenanglah. Mari bicara</font>

102
00:06:24,291 --> 00:06:27,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda selama ini
sudah terlalu kejam pada Ah Ram.</font>

103
00:06:27,731 --> 00:06:29,591
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dan saya yakin Anda
sudah sadar itu.</i></font>

104
00:06:29,991 --> 00:06:31,031
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ah Ram...</i></font>

105
00:06:32,031 --> 00:06:33,361
<font color=#FFFF00>...apa Anda sungguh
ingin dia mati seperti ini?</font>

106
00:06:33,361 --> 00:06:34,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Tutup mulutmu!</font>

107
00:06:36,061 --> 00:06:38,161
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu apa?</font>

108
00:06:38,161 --> 00:06:41,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku... Apa salahku?</font>

109
00:06:42,661 --> 00:06:44,991
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pria tua itu yang jauh
lebih kejam pada anak-anak ini.</i></font>

110
00:06:45,991 --> 00:06:50,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Setidaknya aku memberi makan mereka,
membelikan baju buat mereka...</font>

111
00:06:50,331 --> 00:06:52,431
<font color=#FFFF00>....dan mengizinkan mereka tidur!</font>

112
00:06:53,131 --> 00:06:55,431
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ibu, sakit.</i></font>

113
00:06:59,761 --> 00:07:01,191
<font color=#FFFF00>Kubilang jangan sampai
buat wanita itu terbawa emosi.</font>

114
00:07:01,291 --> 00:07:02,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Soo Jin-ssi.</font>

115
00:07:02,791 --> 00:07:05,731
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa mungkin, apa pernah Anda mengalami
situasi seperti ini sebelumnya?</i></font>

116
00:07:05,731 --> 00:07:07,561
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Maksud saya apa Anda...</i></font>

117
00:07:08,061 --> 00:07:10,231
<font color=#FFFF00>...juga pernah disiksa.../
Diam!</font>

118
00:07:10,431 --> 00:07:12,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bicara seolah
kau mengenalku.</font>

119
00:07:15,461 --> 00:07:18,091
<font color=#FFFF00>Cari tahu tentang keluarga dan
masa kecilnya. Cari apapun sebisamu.</font>

120
00:07:18,091 --> 00:07:19,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau dia diadopsi, aku juga ingin
surat keterangan adopsinya.</font>

121
00:07:21,561 --> 00:07:22,631
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Soo Jin-ssi.</font>

122
00:07:24,261 --> 00:07:25,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya saya sekarang tahu...</font>

123
00:07:26,531 --> 00:07:28,891
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...kenapa Anda terdengar gelisah.</i></font>

124
00:07:29,391 --> 00:07:31,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda saat ini sangat
sengsara, bukan?</font>

125
00:07:31,891 --> 00:07:33,431
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ah Ram bilang pada saya...</i></font>

126
00:07:33,431 --> 00:07:35,891
<font color=#FFFF00>...kalau dia mendengar Anda menangis
setelah bunyi suara xylophone...</font>

127
00:07:35,891 --> 00:07:38,231
<font color=#FFFF00>...waktu suami Anda pulang ke rumah.</font>

128
00:07:39,991 --> 00:07:41,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda juga...</font>

129
00:07:41,831 --> 00:07:43,491
<font color=#FFFF00>...pasti menderita.</font>

130
00:07:46,231 --> 00:07:50,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti bicara omong kosong!</font>

131
00:07:54,261 --> 00:07:57,261
<font color=#FFFF00>Memang beginilah cara
anak-anak harusnya dibesarkan.</font>

132
00:07:57,791 --> 00:07:59,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak-anak itu berisik
dan berantakan.</font>

133
00:07:59,661 --> 00:08:02,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka itu merepotkan!</font>

134
00:08:02,531 --> 00:08:05,091
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ibu, Ibu...</i></font>

135
00:08:05,331 --> 00:08:08,031
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah... Maafkan aku.</font>

136
00:08:08,031 --> 00:08:11,091
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, aku takkan mengulanginya
lagi. Jangan, Ayah.</font>

137
00:08:11,091 --> 00:08:12,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memang diadopsi.</font>

138
00:08:12,931 --> 00:08:14,691
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi aku belum dapat data
apapun soal orang tua angkatnya.</font>

139
00:08:14,691 --> 00:08:17,231
<font color=#FFFF00>Tahun 1997, 1998, 1999...</font>

140
00:08:17,231 --> 00:08:19,361
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia ketahuan lari dari rumah.</font>

141
00:08:19,361 --> 00:08:23,091
<font color=#FFFF00>Tahun 1999, dia dipulangkan kembali ke
rumahnya walau dia mengalami cedera parah.</font>

142
00:08:27,491 --> 00:08:28,631
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh Soo Jin-ssi.</font>

143
00:08:28,831 --> 00:08:32,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya hidup Anda
selama ini sangat berat.</font>

144
00:08:32,361 --> 00:08:36,231
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda mungkin sudah mengalami
cobaan yang tak dapat dibayangkan.</font>

145
00:08:36,331 --> 00:08:37,991
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tiap hari, Anda pasti bertanya
pada diri sendiri...</i></font>

146
00:08:37,991 --> 00:08:41,091
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...kenapa harus Anda sendiri
mengalami semua itu...</i></font>

147
00:08:41,091 --> 00:08:43,201
<font color=#FFFF00>...di saat semua orang lain
hidup bahagia.</font>

148
00:08:44,861 --> 00:08:46,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Hal itu pasti membuat Anda
marah sekali.</font>

149
00:08:47,591 --> 00:08:49,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Kubilang tutup mulutmu.</font>

150
00:08:50,261 --> 00:08:52,491
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Suaranya tiba-tiba merendah.</i></font>

151
00:08:52,631 --> 00:08:54,291
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Artinya dia kehilangan kepercayaan dirinya.</i></font>

152
00:08:55,091 --> 00:08:56,931
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah Ram sudah cerita sebelumnya...</font>

153
00:08:57,091 --> 00:08:59,161
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dia tak berani keluar
meski pintu depan terbuka.</i></font>

154
00:08:59,161 --> 00:09:00,961
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurut Anda kenapa
dia tak berani keluar?</font>

155
00:09:00,961 --> 00:09:02,491
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya...</font>

156
00:09:03,231 --> 00:09:05,291
<font color=#FFFF00>...Anda tahu jawabannya.</font>

157
00:09:43,201 --> 00:09:45,891
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, ampuni aku. Maafkan aku.</font>

158
00:09:45,891 --> 00:09:47,461
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

159
00:09:47,461 --> 00:09:49,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Ampuni aku.</font>

160
00:09:49,791 --> 00:09:51,861
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini semua salahku.</i></font>

161
00:09:57,491 --> 00:09:59,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua perasaan menyakitkan itu.</font>

162
00:09:59,831 --> 00:10:01,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah Ram sedang
merasakan semua itu sekarang.</font>

163
00:10:01,431 --> 00:10:04,491
<font color=#FFFF00>Walau seberapa kalipun kau coba,
kau tak bisa lepas dari penderitaan itu.</font>

164
00:10:05,491 --> 00:10:07,231
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah Ram juga merasakannya sekarang.</font>

165
00:10:07,931 --> 00:10:09,531
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Polisi akan segera tiba.</i></font>

166
00:10:09,531 --> 00:10:12,061
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jika ada apa-apa terjadi
pada Ah Ram...,</i></font>

167
00:10:12,061 --> 00:10:14,131
<font color=#FFFF00>...Anda akan menghabiskan
sisa hidup Anda di penjara.</font>

168
00:10:14,131 --> 00:10:17,931
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong. Lepaskan Ah Ram.</font>

169
00:10:18,031 --> 00:10:21,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika Anda menyerahkan diri,
saya akan berusaha membantu Anda...</font>

170
00:10:21,731 --> 00:10:23,491
<font color=#FFFF00>...agar Anda dapat hidup normal
mulai sekarang.</font>

171
00:10:29,731 --> 00:10:30,861
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu...</font>

172
00:10:39,091 --> 00:10:40,261
<font color=#FFFF00>Sakit...</font>

173
00:10:41,931 --> 00:10:42,991
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

174
00:10:43,791 --> 00:10:45,791
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan Ah Ram.</font>

175
00:10:45,791 --> 00:10:50,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Walau Ibu menyakitiku...,</font>

176
00:10:51,291 --> 00:10:53,161
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku takkan mengeluh
walau ini sakit sekalipun.</font>

177
